</span><br /><span id="victor_an134" class="victor_continuation">team plus the additional number of seconds indicated in the table below according to the place of
</span><br /><span id="victor_an135" class="victor_continuation">their team.
</span><br />
<br /><span id="victor_an136" class="victor_list">20�� for the 2nd team
</span><br /><span id="victor_an137" class="victor_list">30�� for the 3rd team
</span><br /><span id="victor_an138" class="victor_list">40�� for the 4th team
</span><br /><span id="victor_an139" class="victor_list">50�� for the 5th team
</span><br /><span id="victor_an140" class="victor_list">1� for the 6th team
</span><br /><span id="victor_an141" class="victor_list">1�10 for the 7th team
</span><br /><span id="victor_an142" class="victor_list">1�20 for the 8th team
</span><br /><span id="victor_an143" class="victor_list">1�30 for the 9th team
</span><br /><span id="victor_an144" class="victor_list">1�40 for the 10th team
</span><br /><span id="victor_an145" class="victor_list">1�50 for the 11th team
</span><br /><span id="victor_an146" class="victor_list">2�00 for the 12th team
</span><br /><span id="victor_an147" class="victor_list">2�10 for the 13th team
</span><br /><span id="victor_an148" class="victor_list">2�20 for the 14th team
</span><br /><span id="victor_an149" class="victor_list">2�30 for the 15th team
</span><br /><span id="victor_an150" class="victor_list">2�35 for the 16th team
